    dc:description "Fig. 5. Bathycentor kraesselini Saussure, 1892, ♀, lectotype, MNHN (A–G); Ipodoryctes parallellus Granger, 1949, ♀, paralectotype, MNHN (H). A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Head, front view. D. Head, lateral view. E. Mesosoma, dorsal view. F. Mesosoma, lateral view. G. Metasoma, dorsal view. H. Wings." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649693/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649697>
